{
  "stem": "734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And this is where you get dressed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This was the point when something happened, something, in my case, something incredible happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Anton ?] shows up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He was a kapo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that-- He was a kapo in the shower room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And here is this man, I hardly recognized him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I mean--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I mean, I had no idea that he was in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He comes out to make sure that it is I.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because, apparently, he noticed me when they were throwing the clothing articles around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came over to me when I was getting dressed outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, what are you doing here, boy?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This isn't a place for-- for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he walked away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the following day, in the barrack-- we were already assigned to a barrack-- he shows up, flannel shirt, a jacket, socks, underwear, a whole bundle of clothing, and half a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was totally flabbergasted by the sole generosity of this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was more than I ever expected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A jacket, a warm jacket, I mean I looked like-- this was not clothing for a camp, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I looked like I was overdressed, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was almost embarrassed to wear these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, nobody else had such things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- it was really sheer luck to have this happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was-- he had a cruel reputation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean people were afraid of him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Absolutely, they were scared stiff of him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- This barrack I was in could have held about 400 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a huge barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Double bunks, in some cases triple-- but-- triple.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, [? someone-- ?] I do remember one thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came in, I-- I had the upper bunk.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
